<http://example.org/design-grammar#Function> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "What the design object is supposed to achieve — its purpose or design intent. Rules enforce Functions. A Function is realized through Behavior (the computation that achieves it). Connected to Reasoner (as the mechanism evaluating design intent)."@en .
