<http://example.org/design-grammar/valid#ObjectInstance> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Cross-rule identity of a validated geometric element (CMPST-06). The noun — the actual thing in the model that gets validated. Stable across geometry edits. Each ObjectInstance has exactly one ObjState (its current binding snapshot). ID prefix: OI_. Both ObjectInstance and ObjState live above rule scope. Aligned with: sosa:FeatureOfInterest (R3) and geo:Feature (R6)."@en .
