<http://example.org/design-grammar/meta#hasHead> <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment> "Connects a Rule to its head (conclusion) atoms. The head sets the violation flag to true when the body fires. Property: order (integer, 1-indexed). Characteristics: InverseFunctional — each Atom belongs to exactly one Rule's head. Disjoint with hasBody (declared on hasBody side). Equivalent to swrl:head."@en .
